Our lab is just getting started in the Fall of 2025 at the University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign.

We are actively looking for talented and motivated PhD students, postdoctoral researchers, and undergraduates to join us in studying the dynamics of learning in neural circuits.

If you are interested in our research, please see the **[Join Us](/join/)** page for more information on available positions and how to apply.
